，開始留意時事先慢慢知佢講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後再睇翻幾次先發覺佢嘅幽默係神級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幽默唔同搞笑同無厘頭，當然子華嘅演繹另到佢嘅幽默更上一層樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家睇返秋前算帳真係覺好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T12:33:10.000Z","msg":"其中一個show，有一段係講人想唔洗做，勤力d搏升<br />\n但其實升左都係要做到西咁<br />\n<br />\n出黎做野，會有feel"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T12:38:36.000Z","msg":"佢呢段好野 勁在佢完全帶動埋觀眾情緒 同埋佢適當時走埋落台問現場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63affd162244eadc40f07f16ad957de2a640d630","tid":641830,"uid":114692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T12:39:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c75bb1f5ddc0d7976989b331e1b8d08ddf813d3a","tid":641830,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7989b20d0bb5523760feccfbfae4714c98eae255","tid":641830,"uid":9521,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T11:59:43.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得黃子華唔好笑<br />\n聽佢講入面香港咁既情況,我唔明有咩咁好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T12:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實只要明佢講乜,子華講每個事件自已當刻會覺得好笑<br />\n<br />\n但就完場佢再為個整場talk show作總結,全場拍手歡呼後自己步出表演場地,回想整場子華講既野,想想某些位就會苦笑,某些位會唏噓或某些令人得到一些啓發,可能亦會得到一點正能量<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我覺話黃子華既talk show唔係為搞笑而做既表演"},{"pid":"0fc30c1f63cc29d549340475e6c7b79025c412d6","tid":641830,"uid":171863,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:04:58.000Z","msg":"個人愚見，藝術創作者俾人感覺新不如舊係平常事。<br />\n<br />\n以周杰倫為例，如果你問我依家新出的歌好聽D定以前的歌好聽D，相信不單止我，應該有唔少人都會認同以前的作品好聽D。<br />\n<br />\n又例如周星馳，《功夫》、《長江七號》好笑D，定《國產凌凌漆》、《唐伯虎點秋香》好笑D，相信大家心中有數。<br />\n<br />\n當一個藝術創作者到達某個境界，要再闖高峰，自我突破，係非常困難的。<br />\n<br />\n黃子華其實都係一樣。<br />\n<br />\n由第一套作品《娛樂圈血肉史》開始睇起，佢每一套獨自表演的棟篤笑都幾乎睇過，可以咁講，早年的出品多數圍繞某個核心主題，例如《末世財神》講香港人的現實心態、《秋後算帳》講97回歸等等，坐係度睇完成個show，你笑到肚痛，冷靜下來之後，想番佢頭先講過的隻言片語，<br />\n會開始思考：係喎，想深一層，真係好有道理喎。<br />\n<br />\n黃子華之所以咁受歡迎，甚至被稱為神，就係因為佢一直以來的棟篤笑表演，以香港目前的環境來睇，無一個人可以做到佢咁徹底、咁有影響力。<br />\n<br />\n周星馳係一個經典，佢的無厘頭形象深入民心。<br />\n<br />\n黃子華就係另外一個經典，佢的金句一針見血，耐人尋味。<br />\n<br />\n將佢地兩個相比，就好似將兩個米芝蓮名廚放埋一齊，一個擅長中菜，一個擅長西餐，然後討論緊佢地邊個廚藝高D一樣。<br />\n<br />\n以上純粹個人愚見，歡迎討論。<br />\n<br />\n最後，謹祝子華的《金盆𠺘口》演出成功，為佢的棟篤笑系列劃上完美的句號，Good show！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8f5aca6cc586d7dbce2863415da60d864e3cfe","tid":641830,"uid":14548,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:09:29.000Z","msg":"子華fans真係惡過華秀隻狗，D人要幾自大先可以覺得人地係睇唔明/冇文化先唔識笑呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd091a1820e7f9653990fcf1fafdd378f4884797","tid":641830,"uid":2020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:10:14.000Z","msg":"子華講既野 表面睇好好笑 但之後諗返係會慨嘆同苦笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n琴日是旦睇條片講佢以前做演員做臨記 話要比人企定屌一野<br />\n佢講到唔好將自己當主角 生活得無咁辛苦<br />\n<br />\n而家出黎社會做奴隸真係好中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3adbd6160210ae557e6fbcbe1790bade4d2a30c","tid":641830,"uid":175397,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:21:28.000Z","msg":"同Louis ck差幾皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be9ead7ec3c8c3b66004a477bfb6a31aa88343a7","tid":641830,"uid":14548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f3adbd6160210ae557e6fbcbe1790bade4d2a30c","tid":641830,"uid":175397,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:21:28.000Z","msg":"同Louis ck差幾皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:23:33.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a04c2916c28e3090b65aa94da1533cabd12c9970","tid":641830,"uid":126256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71db4bccd14de9e5f0f842fa49a527f06cf31838","tid":641830,"uid":5996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72d7b05bdcdd028fb297d0ed6b21a9842af74ac0","tid":641830,"uid":126256,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T10:46:46.000Z","msg":"呢樣又冇睇 果樣又冇睇咁欣賞d乜<br />\n雖然黃子華呢幾年係唔係好好笑<br />\n但係唔可以推翻佢之前既成就<br />\n星爺係好笑<br />\n但係未到發人深省既地步<br />\n但係黃子華十幾年前既talk show 可以做到<br />\n對港人既習性分析非常到位<br />\n呢個先係佢神既地方"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T11:58:47.000Z","msg":"唔好講到位呢d蝗語啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有非常準/ 非常貼切又唔用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:23:56.000Z","msg":"你岩，sorry"},{"pid":"153db0137c37b4f249fbd954f8bea0bc5bab3fcf","tid":641830,"uid":76488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:25:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3e18efbd58ac8a5c2b8692aa1b6b43b4ef6c566","tid":641830,"uid":85564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdcf6db991349d09ead7ad170731f1566a52db0c","tid":641830,"uid":4525,"like":15,"dislike":49,"score":-34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T09:48:47.000Z","msg":"駁吾刀😂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:36:32.000Z","msg":"有冇埋電話禁極刀？"},{"pid":"60cafa3154571df024bd7cc594c1cc1343b8e849","tid":641830,"uid":50666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:46:18.000Z","msg":"其實拎返佢提出既例子<br />\n若要人不知，係言之有物<br />\n盧海鵬果兩個純搞笑係無meaning"},{"pid":"5aacbd0ecc151ac00f805cc198e2470f818b9181","tid":641830,"uid":82532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be9ead7ec3c8c3b66004a477bfb6a31aa88343a7","tid":641830,"uid":14548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f3adbd6160210ae557e6fbcbe1790bade4d2a30c","tid":641830,"uid":175397,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:21:28.000Z","msg":"同Louis ck差幾皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:23:33.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:49:25.000Z","msg":"我覺得Louis ck好笑好多, 不過偏低俗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5413e15ebabc070248f1ca67fe59d96e173207b9","tid":641830,"uid":115344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T14:01:55.000Z","msg":"佢最高峰應該過左。同意對上兩次都已經唔係咁好笑，但我相信佢最好笑果堆片會long last 多幾個十年<br />\n<br />\n實情係有人吹捧到佢好有深度，有智慧先聽得明，咁你知香港人當然唔會執輸，個個爭住話好好神啊子華神啊咁，突顯下自己<br />\n<br />\n然後進化到人地喝淡水都要起哄，成個教主咁，老實講我認為over左既，同埋希望唔洗棟篤笑唱咁多食字歌，每次我都有點尷尬"},{"pid":"a5c07a13d94aa3dccf4186bc085b9eaed22a6df0","tid":641830,"uid":168534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T14:11:15.000Z","msg":"好笑咪好笑唔好笑咪唔好笑<br />\n何必將自己個套放落人到"},{"pid":"b8cce2b17915305f4bd9e631086f9ba8a2893173","tid":641830,"uid":47470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T14:18:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做乜咁多人覺得周星馳只係無厘頭搞笑冇內涵？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7aa17f32019085f0ed9cb11329f614b8c8a583","tid":641830,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fc30c1f63cc29d549340475e6c7b79025c412d6","tid":641830,"uid":171863,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:04:58.000Z","msg":"個人愚見，藝術創作者俾人感覺新不如舊係平常事。<br />\n<br />\n以周杰倫為例，如果你問我依家新出的歌好聽D定以前的歌好聽D，相信不單止我，應該有唔少人都會認同以前的作品好聽D。<br />\n<br />\n又例如周星馳，《功夫》、《長江七號》好笑D，定《國產凌凌漆》、《唐伯虎點秋香》好笑D，相信大家心中有數。<br />\n<br />\n當一個藝術創作者到達某個境界，要再闖高峰，自我突破，係非常困難的。<br />\n<br />\n黃子華其實都係一樣。<br />\n<br />\n由第一套作品《娛樂圈血肉史》開始睇起，佢每一套獨自表演的棟篤笑都幾乎睇過，可以咁講，早年的出品多數圍繞某個核心主題，例如《末世財神》講香港人的現實心態、《秋後算帳》講97回歸等等，坐係度睇完成個show，你笑到肚痛，冷靜下來之後，想番佢頭先講過的隻言片語，<br />\n會開始思考：係喎，想深一層，真係好有道理喎。<br />\n<br />\n黃子華之所以咁受歡迎，甚至被稱為神，就係因為佢一直以來的棟篤笑表演，以香港目前的環境來睇，無一個人可以做到佢咁徹底、咁有影響力。<br />\n<br />\n周星馳係一個經典，佢的無厘頭形象深入民心。<br />\n<br />\n黃子華就係另外一個經典，佢的金句一針見血，耐人尋味。<br />\n<br />\n將佢地兩個相比，就好似將兩個米芝蓮名廚放埋一齊，一個擅長中菜，一個擅長西餐，然後討論緊佢地邊個廚藝高D一樣。<br />\n<br />\n以上純粹個人愚見，歡迎討論。<br />\n<br />\n最後，謹祝子華的《金盆𠺘口》演出成功，為佢的棟篤笑系列劃上完美的句號，Good show！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T14:34:51.000Z","msg":"好貼切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望今次真係最後同時希望係一個近乎完美既完結 <br />\n相信子華既FANS都會比較希望係最後一次 真係唔想再做落去變得不堪入目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9845b633a2a96e3183e958f693b7994a598b2ea","tid":641830,"uid":104903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T16:20:24.000Z","msg":"逢紅必踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c2fe3decdcdcf570687d8c49cf5fff2d21498fa","tid":641830,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T16:24:17.000Z","msg":"林海峰 一張飛有無試過炒到過萬?"},{"pid":"5b897eb5be433f602cb953b46ca2ff84f7b2367b","tid":641830,"uid":172497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T16:25:41.000Z","msg":"你個username已經答左你啦<br />\n大未必佳<br />\n你個智商係理解唔到子華神諗乜架啦。算把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82bcca14049a6eced7c84a1809b0e044cec4330c","tid":641830,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6969f70d6d4c7d10e90c745eb2e9a445711198f5","tid":641830,"uid":108756,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6e560ade11ebed09d5838f817bd0fb2c5b3b7a7c","tid":641830,"uid":56188,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cite